text: Infection of MDMs with PRRSV caused a 6-fold increase of CXCL-8 secretion after 24 hours (Fig 4) . PRRSV-induced CXCL-8 secretion was significantly inhibited when MDMs were pretreated with tulathromycin (Fig 4) . The positive control LPS, also significantly increased the production of CXCL-8 (Fig 4) .
